<l>iyalpiṉā ṉilvāḻkkai vāḻpava ṉeṉpāṉ</l>
<l>muyalvāru ḷellān talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Among all those who labour (for future happiness) he is greatest who lives well in the household state.</l>
